Class MapData

  • java.lang.Object
    • MapData

  • public class MapData
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    10/3/2018 Lab 11 This is the MapData class that will map the data out for the information given to it from an mdf file. The Class has methods to calculate the statistics, parse the file, create a toString and many other getters and setters to return the value of certain Observation objects when needed.
    Author:
    Matthew Klopfer
